    <!--
      ╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
      ║  NOTASI YOURDON / DeMARCO — KONSISTEN PENUH             ║
      ║                                                          ║
      ║  Entitas Eksternal : rectangle (kotak penuh)            ║
      ║  Proses            : ellipse / bubble                   ║
      ║  Data Store        : DIBANGUN MANUAL dari:              ║
      ║    • garis atas    (mxCell edge/line horizontal)        ║
      ║    • garis bawah   (mxCell edge/line horizontal)        ║
      ║    • label teks    (mxCell vertex, no stroke/fill)      ║
      ║    → hasil: dua garis sejajar = open-ended Yourdon store ║
      ║                                                          ║
      ║  LAYOUT:                                                 ║
      ║    Col A  x=30   Actors      w=140 h=46                 ║
      ║    Col B  x=240  Processes   w=210 h=100                ║
      ║    Col C  x=590  Data Stores w=220                      ║
      ║    Band gap = 210px                                      ║
      ║    Band Y: B1=50  B2=265  B3=480  B4=695               ║
      ╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

      DATA STORE YOURDON — struktur setiap store (contoh D1 di band 1):
        garis atas  : x=590 y=124  w=220 h=0  (horizontal line)
        label teks  : x=590 y=124  w=220 h=44 (no border, no fill, text center)
        garis bawah : x=590 y=168  w=220 h=0  (horizontal line)
        Koneksi arrow masuk ke label (vertex tengah), bukan ke garis
    -->

